WEBVTT

33:54.760 --> 33:56.350 line:80%
Neither of you are taking advantage
of each other.

33:56.350 --> 33:57.810 line:80%
-But...
-My wife's right.

33:57.910 --> 33:59.720 line:80%
You just promised to do

33:59.720 --> 34:00.550 line:80%
whatever I say.

34:00.550 --> 34:01.480 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao...

34:01.480 --> 34:02.280 line:80%
Knock it off!

34:02.720 --> 34:03.590 line:80%
Mr. Zhao.
